sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MutateWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ValidateWH as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RCCtrl as RayCluster Controller
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS:6379 Dash:8265 Client:10001
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Redis as External Redis<br/>6379/TCP Optional mTLS
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Ingress/Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant RayServe as Ray Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        K8sAPI->>MutateWH: Admission Request<br/>Auth: Kubernetes admission
        MutateWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated RayCluster
        K8sAPI->>ValidateWH: Validation Request<br/>Auth: Kubernetes admission
        ValidateWH-->>K8sAPI: Validation OK
        K8sAPI->>RCCtrl: Watch event
        RCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount, Services<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        RCCtrl->>CertMgr: Create Certificate CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        CertMgr-->>RCCtrl: TLS Certificate issued
        RCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod, Worker Pods<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
        K8sAPI->>RayHead: Start Ray head node
        K8sAPI->>RayWorker: Start Ray workers
        RayWorker->>RayHead: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP Optional mTLS
        RayHead->>Redis: Sync cluster state<br/>6379/TCP Optional TLS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
        User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>RCCtrl: Watch event
        RCCtrl->>RayHead: Submit job via Ray Client<br/>10001/TCP gRPC Optional mTLS
        RayHead->>RayHead: Schedule tasks
        RayHead->>RayWorker: Execute tasks<br/>Ray Protocol Optional mTLS
        RayWorker->>RayHead: Task results
        RayHead->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,RayServe: Flow 3: RayService Model Serving
        Client->>Gateway: HTTPS request<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.3 Optional Bearer
        Gateway->>RayServe: HTTP forward<br/>8000/TCP Optional TLS
        RayServe->>RayWorker: Invoke model<br/>Ray Protocol Optional mTLS
        RayWorker-->>RayServe: Prediction result
        RayServe-->>Gateway: HTTP response
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,RCCtrl: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>RCCtrl: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        RCCtrl-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
    end
